SODA — System Offload Dynamics Analyzer
Copyright 2025 Prabhu Vellaisamy, Carnegie Mellon University

This product implements the TaxBreak methodology for decomposing
host-side overhead in LLM inference workloads on CPU-GPU architectures.

If you use this software in academic or industry work, you must cite:

